Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.28,0:00:04.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我杀的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.07,0:00:07.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缤纷小鸟的翅膀不再纯净
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.15,0:00:11.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我将长得很像黄泉的女生…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.32,0:00:13.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经无法再飞翔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.64,0:00:16.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经…
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.67,0:03:59.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.84,0:04:10.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真透  你一定很痛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.50,0:04:12.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真透  辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.21,0:04:15.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真透  快回来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.69,0:04:19.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真透  真透
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.10,0:04:24.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真透  真透  真透…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.60,0:04:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.34,0:04:34.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Black  Rock  Shooter…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.64,0:04:50.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.62,0:04:57.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙耶  怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.64,0:05:01.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你都做了些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.29,0:05:06.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通过给少女们带来最大的精神负担
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.19,0:05:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让那个世界的少女们消除仅存的一点人性
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.06,0:05:13.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使其真实的力量苏醒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.09,0:05:17.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我给小鸟游带来压力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.35,0:05:20.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让DEAD  MASTER觉醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.91,0:05:25.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你却将Black  Rock  Shooter…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.06,0:05:30.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没想到  真透会被困住了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.87,0:05:34.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想通过让真透接触那个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.80,0:05:38.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让Black  Rock  Shooter苏醒  这样的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.81,0:05:40.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.49,0:05:45.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Black  Rock  Shooter会把那个世界破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.74,0:05:49.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话你知道属于我们的她会有什么影响吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.54,0:05:51.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.31,0:05:57.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去  大家都很痛苦  沙耶也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.16,0:05:58.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.31,0:06:00.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙耶…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.38,0:06:07.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今  干脆在这里把黑衣杀掉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.39,0:06:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等  等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.77,0:06:23.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么可能下手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.50,0:06:28.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑衣同学是无辜的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.29,0:06:33.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能下得了手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.07,0:07:54.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑衣同学被困在Black  Rock  Shooter里了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.21,0:07:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙耶…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.41,0:08:00.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要呼唤Black  Rock  Shooter里的黑衣同学
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.15,0:08:04.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能把声音传达给她  说不定就能…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.45,0:08:05.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不能去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.86,0:08:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.14,0:08:11.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你要记住  我最优先保护的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.31,0:08:14.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是黑衣  而是属于我们的她
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.66,0:08:29.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛苦吧  难过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.50,0:08:35.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑衣同学
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.07,0:08:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑衣同学  求求你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.23,0:08:47.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑衣同学  听听我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.78,0:09:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是黑衣同学吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.23,0:09:06.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.29,0:09:10.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要听见
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.53,0:09:18.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我遇见了她
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.30,0:09:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟她的故事  从那个夏天开始
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.45,0:09:26.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好热
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.44,0:09:42.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.91,0:09:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.32,0:09:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来我家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.50,0:09:59.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听我的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.30,0:10:05.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  快吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.46,0:10:09.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用客气的  快
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.67,0:10:26.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  有没有冰棍呢  冰棍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.52,0:10:31.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是三丁目神足家的孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.76,0:10:33.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  你认识她吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.59,0:10:37.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很出名的  因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.32,0:10:40.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论在学校还是在家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.46,0:10:45.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优都承受着我无法想象的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.03,0:10:51.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此  她都一一挺过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.43,0:10:59.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切的痛苦都靠小小的身体来承受
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.64,0:11:02.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.49,0:11:06.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得不能对她置之不理
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.06,0:11:10.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小优很强
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.11,0:11:12.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很强？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.68,0:11:14.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我很羡慕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.44,0:11:18.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不像我只会为了芝麻绿豆的小事而烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.38,0:11:21.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很厉害  很尊敬你
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
