Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.44,0:11:30.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有另一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.21,0:11:33.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在优被欺负
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.88,0:11:36.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遇到悲伤的事的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.74,0:11:37.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是优
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.12,0:11:39.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有另一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.68,0:11:42.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出现  代替优
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.82,0:11:45.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,承受痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.42,0:11:52.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  优并不那么痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.74,0:12:06.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我心想不能让这孩子孤单一人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.76,0:12:10.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是能为优做点什么的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.19,0:12:21.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是能为优承担一些伤害的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.39,0:12:30.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.45,0:12:33.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个不是麦茶  是素面的酱汁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.19,0:12:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙耶  小优的家…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.82,0:12:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小优！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.72,0:13:13.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我心想
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.63,0:13:19.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是优干的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.59,0:13:23.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是优开始向折磨自己的事物复仇了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.58,0:13:31.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认为这是我做的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.90,0:13:35.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小优…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.68,0:13:48.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  上车吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.61,0:13:54.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小优
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.38,0:14:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.93,0:14:01.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.33,0:14:04.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这样的  小优
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.46,0:14:07.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.09,0:14:19.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小优！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.86,0:14:27.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火灾的起因是小优的义父忘记掐灭的烟头
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.73,0:14:37.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无法忘记那份笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.33,0:14:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要怎么样…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.33,0:14:44.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才能补偿优呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.88,0:14:46.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎么样…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.91,0:15:01.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小优…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.39,0:15:16.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.35,0:15:21.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小优  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.74,0:15:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的不是你想的那样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.70,0:15:26.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想一直都做小优的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.38,0:15:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.06,0:15:35.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能原谅我  我什么都愿意做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.28,0:15:37.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.43,0:15:46.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有一个世界会比活在这个世界更痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.98,0:15:48.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小优…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.32,0:15:54.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次又在想什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.92,0:15:57.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会做什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.32,0:16:00.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我讨厌痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.12,0:16:06.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  要不要让那个人承受一下呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.26,0:16:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这份痛楚…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.06,0:16:12.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  这是怎么了  小优
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.05,0:16:16.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你愿意为我做任何事  是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.44,0:16:18.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.02,0:16:23.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  请保护我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.57,0:16:25.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保护是指…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.52,0:16:33.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼唤自己的名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.38,0:16:35.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙耶？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.97,0:16:36.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.19,0:16:38.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一个名字
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.51,0:16:41.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一个名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.05,0:16:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.65,0:16:52.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Black  Gold  Saw
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.48,0:17:10.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快醒过来  黑衣同学
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.48,0:17:13.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.25,0:18:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙耶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.93,0:18:56.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.63,0:19:07.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是她保护了我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.26,0:19:09.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,属于我们的她
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.09,0:19:12.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.63,0:19:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明对她做了很过分的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.23,0:19:17.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.53,0:19:24.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了  沙耶被原谅了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.50,0:19:29.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么都做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.66,0:19:31.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.01,0:19:34.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明必须保护好的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.71,0:19:36.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须保护好那个世界的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.00,0:19:38.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.68,0:19:40.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不够啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.94,0:19:42.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经足够了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.09,0:19:48.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙耶…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.24,0:19:52.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  沙耶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.02,0:19:56.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  真透
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.93,0:19:58.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.78,0:20:04.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在你一定很痛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.55,0:20:09.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在你一定很难过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.92,0:20:15.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  真透
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.13,0:20:23.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  Black  Rock  Shooter
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.42,0:20:32.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把我的愿望强加给你们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.93,0:20:35.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又痛苦  又难过
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.54,0:20:39.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我终于明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.34,0:20:45.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这份痛苦一直都由别人替我承担着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.97,0:20:47.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心灵的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.59,0:20:50.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一个自己永远都在战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.83,0:20:54.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背负着我们的烦恼和混乱的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.75,0:20:56.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后在战斗中另一个自己最终死去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.07,0:20:59.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些烦恼和感情才会最终消失
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.74,0:21:04.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝色眼睛的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.27,0:21:07.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使伤害别人也要继续战斗下去的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.09,0:21:11.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是为了把我们从烦恼中解救出来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.11,0:21:14.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.14,0:21:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…不是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.81,0:21:43.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄泉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.21,0:21:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.15,0:21:52.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,篝  没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.05,0:21:55.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.71,0:21:59.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.38,0:22:01.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得心里不太平静
